It's the map you love, but not mine, and fixed.

FIXES IN THIS MAP: Well, the "wall" is gone. So you could actually try to finish the level.

**IMPORTANT: The original map wasn't made by me. It was made by G.o.d.W.a.n.4. . I just fixed it. So all credit should go to him, not me. Please check him out and thank him for an awesome map.
